{"tid":838814,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"［突發］今日又有係OL抄我牌","createTime":"2018-09-27T11:54:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-27T15:23:49.000Z","uid":8968,"like":11,"dislike":155,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"8b353363937b4a0d8bf2e095b313b49cda0397e0","tid":838814,"uid":8968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T11:54:28.000Z","msg":"是甘的<br />\n小弟做開物流管理員<br />\n今日派左去個新地區<br />\n一上去就有個約165高D cup仲要著短裙既reception 開門，樣都有幾分似林凱恩<br />\n<br />\n我二話不說單手托起件1kg既貨<br />\n之後見到佢面紅紅咁<br />\n就放低係佢枱面<br />\n之後話「唔該」<br />\n講完見到佢打左個冷震<br />\n之後佢就話「可...可唔可以俾你電話我」<br />\n我二話不說，頭也不回開門走<br />\n（但禁錯左掣，屌）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n聽日又好似要去佢公司<br />\n我應該點做"},{"pid":"cc8855b0142e7dca859fd7f47a2ee846d10d1c4e","tid":838814,"uid":40965,"like":36,"dislike":1,"score":35,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T11:55:36.000Z","msg":"係咪90講句野都疾下疾下<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe7dddc76ac4305dfcfb7bbf2a04246acb2f61b6","tid":838814,"uid":130732,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T11:55:51.000Z","msg":"1.5/10<br />\n重作"},{"pid":"111ad5952b04ca86e5b69368f0d3250547f4bc34","tid":838814,"uid":8968,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"cc8855b0142e7dca859fd7f47a2ee846d10d1c4e","tid":838814,"uid":40965,"like":36,"dislike":1,"score":35,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T11:55:36.000Z","msg":"係咪90講句野都疾下疾下<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/f